</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><i>-ik</i> (<i>-ig</i> in Late Middle Persian)</td>
<td>Having to do with, having the nature of, made of, caused by, similar to</td>
<td>English <i>-ic</i>, Latin <i>-icus</i>, Greek <i>â€“ikos</i>, Slavic <i>-isku</i></td>
<td><i>PÄrsÄ«k</i> 'Persian', <i>Ä€sÅrik</i> 'Assyrian', <i>Pahlavik</i> 'Parthian', <i>HrÅmÄyÄ«k/HrÅmÄ«k</i> 'Byzantine, Roman', <i>TÄzÄ«k</i> 'Arab'
